  <chapter xml:id="overview">
    <title>Mission Overview</title>
    <para>This handbook enumerates observation procedures. It is synchronized with
      <link xlink:href="stellar-observation.jats">JATS observation records</link>,
      the <link xlink:href="explorer-journal.fb2">Explorer Journal</link>,
      and the <link xlink:href="mission-summary.metamd">MetaMarkdown summary</link>.</para>
    <para>Before each shift, review the <link xlink:href="mission-operations.creole">Mission Operations Guide</link>
      and cross-check anomaly tickets within the <link xlink:href="mission-wiki.wiki">Mission Wiki</link>.</para>
    <section xml:id="assets">
      <title>Referenced Assets</title>
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Star tracker alignment tables reside in <link xlink:href="engineering-notes.rst">Engineering Notes</link>
            and <link xlink:href="engineering-notes.rest">reStructuredText REST mirror</link>.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>Observation network diagrams: <link xlink:href="mission-network.dot">DOT</link>,
            <link xlink:href="mission-network.gv">Graphviz</link>, and <link xlink:href="mission-flowchart.mermaid">Mermaid flow</link>.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>Mission bibliographies maintained in <link xlink:href="orbital-research.bib">BibTeX</link>,
            <link xlink:href="orbital-research-extended.bibtex">Extended BibTeX</link>,
            and <link xlink:href="mission-citations.csljson">CSL JSON</link>.</para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>
  </chapter>

  <chapter xml:id="field-operations">
    <title>Field Operations</title>
    <para>When entering observational data, use the following structure.</para>
    <section>
      <title>Checklist</title>
      <orderedlist>
        <listitem><para>Confirm voice briefings are logged in <link xlink:href="crew-briefing.rtf">Crew Briefing</link>.</para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>Annotate spectral anomalies in <link xlink:href="observatory-log.dj">Observatory Log (DJ)</link> and its DJOT variant.</para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>Synchronize telemetry windows described in <link xlink:href="telemetry-events.jsonl">telemetry-events.jsonl</link>.</para></listitem>
      </orderedlist>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Resource Allocation</title>
      <para>The resource plan is stored in both <link xlink:href="resource-allocation.tsv">TSV</link>
        and <link xlink:href="resource-allocation.tab">TAB</link> formats for compatibility with navigation planning tools.</para>
    </section>
  </chapter>

